Hello there, Welcome!

I am a Doctoral Candidate at Department of Earth & Environment at Boston University.

I investigate large-scale ocean atmosphere interactions associated with Kuroshio Extension variations and their linkages with marine heatwaves, advised by Prof. Bruce Anderson.
